'''叙利亚共和国卫队'''是一支由2万多官兵（2011年）所组成的[[装甲部队|装甲部队]]，负责保卫首都[[大马士革|大马士革]]的安全。它是叙利亚唯一允许在首都活动的军事力量<ref name=MEIB2>{{cite journal|last=MEIB|title=Syria's Praetorian Guards: A Primer|journal=Middle East Intelligence Bulletin|volume=2|issue=7|url=http://www.meforum.org/meib/articles/0008_s2.htm|accessdate=20 July 2011|date=2000|archive-date=2012-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704135413/http://www.meforum.org/meib/articles/0008_s2.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 历史 ==
1976年，叙利亚共和国卫队成立之初，是一支由1万人组成的特种装甲部队，起初是为了防止[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]境内反叙利亚的[[巴勒斯坦解放组织|巴勒斯坦解放组织]]武装分支袭击叙利亚。1982年巴解被逐出黎巴嫩后，叙利亚共和国卫队的任务转变为保护叙利亚政府及[[叙利亚阿拉伯复兴社会党|叙利亚阿拉伯复兴社会党]]官员免遭外部威胁<ref>{{cite book|last=Paul|first=James|title=Human rights in Syria|year=1990|publisher=Human Rights Watch|pages=50|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=N-xjxWYWnlwC&pg=PA50&dq=syrian+%22republican+guard%22&hl=en&ei=wvImTt_FLY31sga0vOyPCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8&ved=0CEsQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=%22republican%20guard%22&f=false|access-date=2011-12-24|archive-date=2014-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101234308/http://books.google.com/books?id=N-xjxWYWnlwC&pg=PA50&dq=syrian+%22republican+guard%22&hl=en&ei=wvImTt_FLY31sga0vOyPCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=8&ved=0CEsQ6AEwBw#v=onepage&q=%22republican%20guard%22&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

为了使卫队士兵绝对忠诚于叙利亚当局，卫队所有官兵都必须是来自叙利亚西部的[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]][[穆斯林|穆斯林]]。卫队的指挥官可轻松获得来自于[[代尔祖尔|代尔祖尔]]的[[石油|石油]]出售收益，而这部分开支占据了叙利亚国家预算支出的很大部分<ref>{{cite book|last=Batatu|first=Hanna|title=Syria's peasantry, the descendants of its lesser rural notables, and their politics|year=1999|publisher=Princeton Univ. Press|location=Princeton, NJ|page=237|isbn=0691002541|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Mbr-ZfU_uCoC&pg=PA237&dq=syrian+%22republican+guard%22&hl=en&ei=wvImTt_FLY31sga0vOyPCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=syrian%20%22republican%20guard%22&f=false|access-date=2011-12-24|archive-date=2014-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101234317/http://books.google.com/books?id=Mbr-ZfU_uCoC&pg=PA237&dq=syrian+%22republican+guard%22&hl=en&ei=wvImTt_FLY31sga0vOyPCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q=syrian%20%22republican%20guard%22&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

许多[[阿萨德家族|阿萨德家族]]的成员都曾在叙利亚共和国卫队中服役。现任总统[[巴沙尔·阿萨德|巴沙尔·阿萨德]]曾于1994至1999年担任该卫队中的一名[[上校|上校]]，並且指挥着其中的一个[[旅|旅]]。他弟弟[[马赫尔·阿萨德|马赫尔·阿萨德]]也曾经担任卫队的上校，自2000年起，统率着该卫队<ref>{{cite paper |last=Bar |first=Shmuel |url=http://www.herzliyaconference.org/_Uploads/2590Bashars.pdf |title=Bashar’s Syria: The Regime and its Strategic Worldview |date=2006 |pages=379, 384 |accessdate=2011-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723214138/http://www.herzliyaconference.org/_Uploads/2590Bashars.pdf |archivedate=2011-07-23 |journal= }}</ref>。

